{"tid":157271,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKGBuddies]GFRIEND討論區(40) 交出你的腎給女友吧!R","createTime":"2017-03-15T11:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T18:25:57.000Z","uid":83632,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1361c1588a8af9cc92d0c2cde2bdcea8de45dbbe","tid":157271,"uid":83632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"#1<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎黎到G-Friend 討論區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></span><br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Kim So Jung！Jung Ye Rin！Jung Eun Bi！<br />\nChoi Yu Na！Hwang Eun Bi！Kim Ye Won！<br />\n <br />\nYeo！ Ja ！Chin！ Gu！</span></span></div><br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67gk2Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67gk2Z.jpg&h=385f3dc5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/BxpN7FfCIAAy3oV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FBxpN7FfCIAAy3oV.jpg&h=d4693d10&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://postfiles4.naver.net/MjAxNzAzMDZfMjI3/MDAxNDg4NzYxNDc3OTYy.qfcri4Wh4jLCfQ50_F5r_nvJ-xqd2Z7cQPNRAtKRHrog.D4zZbyOU_kBOK9qQG13aarVXbPSDZ0EXglVxBF6lwZMg.JPEG.muzmon/3676v-001.jpg?type=w966\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpostfiles4.naver.net%2FMjAxNzAzMDZfMjI3%2FMDAxNDg4NzYxNDc3OTYy.qfcri4Wh4jLCfQ50_F5r_nvJ-xqd2Z7cQPNRAtKRHrog.D4zZbyOU_kBOK9qQG13aarVXbPSDZ0EXglVxBF6lwZMg.JPEG.muzmon%2F3676v-001.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw966&h=851bb844&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://cdnimg.melon.co.kr/resource/image/cds/musicstory/imgUrl20170303033433364.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdnimg.melon.co.kr%2Fresource%2Fimage%2Fcds%2Fmusicstory%2FimgUrl20170303033433364.jpg&h=5c7b8b1e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://postfiles6.naver.net/MjAxNzAzMDZfMTAg/MDAxNDg4NzY5MjcwMDQ3.3yKAGoitkoBSXW5jGmDVMSCWnBosoeDAtfTwtF7ku1wg.KMbC5nGCQWZZ9qmAopBMC0g5Twd3WthMHg9a1M4SXqAg.GIF.muzmon/1.gif?type=w966\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpostfiles6.naver.net%2FMjAxNzAzMDZfMTAg%2FMDAxNDg4NzY5MjcwMDQ3.3yKAGoitkoBSXW5jGmDVMSCWnBosoeDAtfTwtF7ku1wg.KMbC5nGCQWZZ9qmAopBMC0g5Twd3WthMHg9a1M4SXqAg.GIF.muzmon%2F1.gif%3Ftype%3Dw966&h=a1ba7e82&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5wR081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5wR081.jpg&h=b5904a69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08Y5R3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08Y5R3.jpg&h=a42891bc&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o6ZtchayBITIz74E8/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o6ZtchayBITIz74E8%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3d69e633&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\nGFRIEND（韓語：여자친구）是Source Music於2015年推出的韓國六人女子音樂組合，<br />\n成員包括Sowon、Yerin、Eunha、Yuju、SinB和Umji。<br />\n <br />\n2014年10月30日，Source Music公開將於11月推出6人女團。同日，官網介紹4位成員: Sowon、Yerin、SinB、Umji。GFRIEND出道延遲至2015年。<br />\n2015年1月5日，Source Music通過官網公布GFRIEND出道日，並公開成員Eunha和Yuju。11日後的1月16日正式出道。粉絲名為Buddy(Buddies)。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://33.media.tumblr.com/d7e1467bf3074848431efd344b9327ba/tumblr_nmxh6dJZXF1ro5y21o1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F33.media.tumblr.com%2Fd7e1467bf3074848431efd344b9327ba%2Ftumblr_nmxh6dJZXF1ro5y21o1_500.gif&h=ce619b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你和我，畢地與女朋友</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n#2.1<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成員資料：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>So Won</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/837324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F837324.jpg&h=d6a3a31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4P1948.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4P1948.jpg&h=c8f79257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝名：Sowon(소원)<br />\n本名：金紹(/韶)情 / 감소정/ Kim So Jung<br />\n生日：1995年12月07日（21歲）<br />\n身高：172.8cm<br />\n血型：A型<br />\n星座：射手座<br />\n出生地：首爾<br />\n學歷：誠信女子大學媒體影像演技學系(在學中)<br />\n隊內擔當：隊長、主Rapper、副唱、黃金比例擔當<br />\n專長：走秀、時尚搭配<br />\n興趣：烹飪、看電影<br />\n <br />\n個人經歷：<br />\n2011年 Rainbow〈To Me〉MV (客串)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqvdj0Fl_MY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxqvdj0Fl_MY&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4ed944c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqvdj0Fl_MY</a><br />\n <br />\nSowon身材比例 SHOWCASE<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzGzTrl21nw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFzGzTrl21nw&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4302a245\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzGzTrl21nw</a><br />\n <br />\n仙氣與廁紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gShnLdKto6I\" data-